Description: Handle of Koan pottery transport amphora. Rectangular stamp; club symbol.
Curator's comments: Only known from Griffiths' drawing in Petrie's Journal, 1884-5, p.188a, 15. Not specified if it is a double-barrel handle. No parallel is known.
Bibliographic references: Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (JB.0102)
